metadata.name: Galaxy Cat Eclipse
metadata.description:
#1 Galaxy Cat

Black cats are well known by their mysterious backgrounds
Some think that there more sensitive to humans feelings and emotions
This collection is inspired by these graceful animals and shows the world inside of them.

The collection contains 5 different cat eclipses named:

Lunar, Solar, Galaxy

Jupiter and Saturn will be released in January 2022

The artwork combines a unique photograph of authors black cat and digital editing.

Collector will receive: 
MP4 6sec video
Original digital still artwork in PNG 3975x5565
